prompts.frontCover:
A watercolor painting of a humorous birthday card front cover, flat 2D for printing. Two specific people, a man and a woman, are featured as cartoon characters based on the reference image [3fae79ed-26aa-413f-9a7a-1e740572efdb]. The man, with short dark hair and glasses, and the woman, with shoulder-length dark hair, are depicted in a lighthearted, funny scenario: they are comically tangled up in a huge, unwieldy pile of birthday presents and wrapping paper, maybe one is tripping over a ribbon. Their expressions are of playful surprise and laughter. The background is a clean, simple wash of soft pastel colors. In the center of the design, the word "birthday" is written in a beautiful, readable, handwritten cursive script. The artwork has a distinct watercolor style with soft flowing colors, visible artistic brushstrokes, a subtle paper texture, and organic paint bleeds along the edges of the characters and objects.

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
